%% MyAIStorybook - Sequence Diagram: Character Chat Interaction

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend as Frontend<br/>(Next.js)
    participant Backend as FastAPI<br/>Backend
    participant Chatbot as ChatbotAgent
    participant LLM as Ollama<br/>LLM
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    
    User->>Frontend: Select character to chat with
    activate Frontend
    
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/chat<br/>{story_id, character_name, user_message}
    activate Backend
    
    Backend->>DB: Get story data
    activate DB
    DB-->>Backend: Story with characters
    deactivate DB
    
    Backend->>Chatbot: chat(story_context, character, message)
    activate Chatbot
    
    Chatbot->>Chatbot: Build character prompt with story context
    
    Chatbot->>LLM: Generate character response<br/>(2-4 sentences, child-friendly)
    activate LLM
    LLM-->>Chatbot: Character response
    deactivate LLM
    
    Chatbot-->>Backend: Response text
    deactivate Chatbot
    
    Backend->>DB: Save conversation<br/>(conversation_id, messages)
    activate DB
    DB-->>Backend: Saved
    deactivate DB
    
    Backend-->>Frontend: {response, character}
    deactivate Backend
    
    Frontend->>Frontend: Display character response in chat interface
    Frontend-->>User: Show character message
    deactivate Frontend
